column3: This tee allows kids to move, play, and stay comfortable all day. The soft cotton blend feels great on the skin, while the added stretch keeps up with every movement. Add an all-over design to create a piece you won’t find anywhere else. Order this tee for your child or sell it online with no minimums. 96% cotton, 4% elastane. Fabric weight: 5. 6 oz. /yd. ² (189 g/m²). Soft handfeel with a smooth surface for vibrant prints. Regular fit. Self-fabric collar. Tear-away care label. Pilling-resistant and colorfast after washing. Blank product sourced from Mexico. Disclaimers:. Avoid large solid fills of dark or saturated colors. These areas require more ink, which can make the fabric feel stiff on first wear and appear slightly muted after printing. Lighter tones use less ink and feel softer on first wear, but you are not limited to them. To reduce stiffness, use patterns or designs with negative space instead of solid fills. Less ink makes the fabric feel softer and more breathable. Expect slightly muted color results compared to digital previews or sublimation prints. Cotton absorbs ink differently, so the fabric’s texture may show through the print, adding a soft, matte finish. When stretched, printed areas may show fine cracks or the white base fabric, especially at seams, cuffs, or tight spots. This is normal for flexible cotton garments. Print results may vary slightly by garment thickness. Thicker fabrics absorb ink differently from lighter items. Product code: 5103KCO. This product is made on demand. No minimums.
